message.body: Did you guys make it down yet?
We are running late. Had to get cronuts and hunter stops like every 20 minutes for treats!
Probably be there at 3. We are jammin to white zombie haha
Nice. So excited for a cronut.
Our place was all out so we had to drive to South philly. They aren't exactly the same but still good.
We made it to dads! He's gonna take us to a spot so hunter can shoot his new fun
Gun
Okay im out of work in 8 mins. Should i just come over there? Id be there by 6
Yeah come on over! That will be enough shooting for me
Omg that cronut was delicious! Thank you!!! Thank you again for dinner too. I really appreciate it :)

I forgot to give you yr lapis from Chile!! I'll leave it with dad.
Dad is laughing that you ate it already!
Lapis!!! Thank you!!!!
Lok, I couldnt resist!
Lol

Theres the knotty pine, ld's pancake house(where i usually go) and front royal diner

Yeah. L dees is in main street
L dees?
If you go down 340 until you get to the courthouse and take a right at the light on main street. Go all the way to the end and its on the left
